<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>r</expan>, uns hat <expan>fürgel<ex>egt</ex></expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> Hebenstreit, unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie im ewr geleitsman czü
                                <expan>Potenstet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>czwo</add> lageln mit raynvail <expan>aufgehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab,
                        darumb daz er bey <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> weinen <add>eins</add>
                        czeichens <add>cze wenig</add> gehabt süll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Nu
                        spricht <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> unser, daz er das
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> gehandelt hab und hab auch
                                <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> geleitsman czü Erfürt von
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> weynen gerichtet und schon
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, was davon gepürt, und sey das
                        czeichen <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> versawmt worden.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dienst willen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden schicken wöllet, daz dem
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein weine von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        geleitsman <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>golt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
